% @MIMAGE
%
% Files
%   MImage       - Constructor of @MImage
%   convert2gray - Convert the color image to a gray image
%   demo         - Demo the @MImage class
%   display      - Display the @MImage object
%   fliplr       - Flip the MImage from left to right
%   flipud       - Flip the MImage from up to down
%   gaussblur    - Blur a MImage with a Gaussian filter
%   get          - Get properties of the @MImage object
%   imadjust     - Enhance the @MImage
%   imgradient   - Compute the image gradient of the @MImage
